        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <img class="featurette-image img-responsive mx-auto" src="~/images/SSAll-Devices.png" style="width:100%; height:100%; " />
        </div>
    </div>


    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <div class="row featurette">
        <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading" style="color:#123274">Share your files. With friends, family and colleagues.</h2>
            <p class="lead">You can invite others quickly and easily to view and download any desired file. No more e-mail attachments needed!</p>
        </div>
